      "updated": 1738195200000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "FR-025..FR-028  device PAT issue/scope/revoke; agent runs metered (proxy) or BYOK  -  SC-008 every metered token deducted at the gateway  -  SC-009 tool calls audited\nMode A routes all model calls through the single LLM Gateway chokepoint (credits + trace). Mode B uses the agent's own key (unmetered) but tools still pass the MCP allowlist + RLS.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "FR-025..FR-028  device PAT issue/scope/revoke; agent runs metered (proxy) or BYOK  -  SC-008 every metered token deducted at the gateway  -  SC-009 tool calls audited\nMode A routes all model calls through the single LLM Gateway chokepoint (credits + trace). Mode B uses the agent's own key (unmetered) but tools still pass the MCP allowlist + RLS.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
